headline: Amazon and 9 More Stocks to Buy for 2026
summary: Barron’s capitalized on the trends with  Alibaba Group Holding Alphabet  and  ASML Holding  as well as other winners, including  Citigroup  and  Uber Technologies  in our top 10 picks for 2025.  Rounding out the list is pharmaceutical turnaround candidate  Bristol Myers Squibb  which yields almost 5%.
